42
00:02:00.958 --> 00:02:03.498
And there, regarding mobility, what is it?

43
00:02:03.498 --> 00:02:07.398
The master of mobility is the diaphragm.

44
00:02:08.798 --> 00:02:12.138
That's why we will learn how this diaphragm is built.

45
00:02:12.878 --> 00:02:17.078
One day, he taught me, he said, Marc, one day, you will feel the power in the tissue.

46
00:02:17.938 --> 00:02:20.158
For me, the concept of power was very intellectual.

47
00:02:23.848 --> 00:02:26.768
At the same time, intellectually, I tell myself yes, I can understand that there is a kind of...

48
00:02:26.768 --> 00:02:29.928
