49
00:02:30.928 --> 00:02:31.768
It doesn't stop.

50
00:02:33.708 --> 00:02:35.408
There's an incredible power; it's astounding.

51
00:02:36.028 --> 00:02:39.948
And he tells me sometimes, in the still points, in certain fulcrums, the power is there too.

52
00:02:40.128 --> 00:02:41.448
It's incredible; there you can...

